lead_paragraph: Matthew Fisher-Davis tied his career-high with 20 points, and Vanderbilt upset No. 16 Kentucky 74-62 on Saturday for their third straight victory.

headline.print_headline: Fisher-Davis Scores 20 as Vandy Upsets No. 16 Kentucky 74-62
